{"tid":1238794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊：沒武器「第二排」衝擊警方示威者亦可被控暴動罪","createTime":"2019-06-18T02:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T09:24:58.000Z","uid":30647,"like":22,"dislike":647,"uniUserReply":121,"replies":[{"pid":"f287791d86f0ea271ad8e6e6da269dd9101d30bb","tid":1238794,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:58:10.000Z","msg":"警務處長盧偉聰昨晩（17日）澄清，只是稱上周三（12日）反修訂《逃犯條例》示威衝突中，有一小部分人行為涉嫌干犯暴動罪，不是說整個示威是暴動。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">身兼資深大律師的行政會議成員湯家驊今早（18日）表示，示威者當時即使手上沒武器，但若配上頭盔等裝備，在「第二排」跟著前面示威者衝擊警察防線，都有可能被控暴動罪，因他們當時都有破壞社會安寧的意圖；他指出，2016年旺角騷亂後，法庭已有同類案例</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\nfrom Mingpao<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190618/s00001/1560824890594/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A-%E6%B2%92%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%E3%80%8C%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%8E%92%E3%80%8D%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E4%BA%A6%E5%8F%AF%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190618%2Fs00001%2F1560824890594%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%25A9%258A-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%258E%2592%25E3%2580%258D%25E8%25A1%259D%25E6%2593%258A%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BA%25A6%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXmaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=8014401b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190618%2Fs00001%2F1560824890594%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D